&lt;/h2>&lt;p>저희 프로젝트는 크게 3개의 서브넷을 가지게 됩니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Kubernetes Subnet
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Kubernetes Master, Worker nodes&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Storage Subnet
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>NFS Server&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>DevOps Subnet
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Jenkins Server&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
